l's  Alice's Adventures in Wonderland (  1865 ) and Through the Looking Glass (  1872 ), who was based on his child friend  Alice Liddell , daughter of the Dean of Christ Church, Oxford."],"variants":[{"name":"Alys","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Alice ."]},{"name":"Alis","meanings":["equivalent of <b>Alice</b> ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Lady Alice Ribemont was born in 1253, in Ribemont, Aisne, Picardie, France as the daughter of Sir Wistache de Ribemont and Lady Alice de Fontaine. She married Sir William de Giffard II about 1272. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. She died in 1273, in Exeter, Exeter, Devon, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 20, and was buried in Exeter, Exeter, Devon, England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"1253–1273":"1253–1273","1250–1329":"1250–1329","1273–1361":"1273–1361","–Male":"Surnud","1220–1290":"1220–1290","about 1272":"umbes 1272","1253":"1253","1220":"1220","1273":"1273","1361":"1361","1250":"1250","1329":"1329","1290":"1290","Ribemont Castle, Aisne, Picardie, France":"Ribemont, Aisne, Picardie, Prantsusmaa","Ribemont, Aisne, Picardie, France":"Ribemont, Aisne, Picardie, Prantsusmaa","Exeter, Exeter, Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Exeter, Exeter, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1253–1273":"1253–1273","1250–1329":"1250–1329","1273–1361":"1273–1361","–Male":"Kuollut","1220–1290":"1220–1290","about 1272":"noin 1272","1253":"1253","1220":"1220","1273":"1273","1361":"1361","1250":"1250","1329":"1329","1290":"1290","Ribemont Castle, Aisne, Picardie, France":"Ribemont, Aisne, Picardie, Ranska","Ribemont, Aisne, Picardie, France":"Ribemont, Aisne, Picardie, Ranska","Exeter, Exeter, Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Exeter, Exeter, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1253–1273":"1253–1273","1250–1329":"1250–1329","1273–1361":"1273–1361","–Male":"Décédé","1220–1290":"1220–1290","about 1272":"environ 1272","1253":"1253","1220":"1220","1273":"1273","1361":"1361","1250":"1250","1329":"1329","1290":"1290","Ribemon